<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72943" title="Desperate Housewives - 8x01-c" src="http://static.sorozatjunkie.hu/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Desperate-Housewives-8x01-c.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="269" />

